data.description: One level living at its finest! Enjoy the convenience of living minutes from the highway and dining/shopping but also being at the end of a quiet road. This 3-bedroom 1.5 bath brick home is a must see. Enjoy entertaining in the large front yard or fully fenced in back yard! Open concept living/dining/kitchen, perfect for guests to enjoy your new home. Schedule your showing today and be moved in before the holidays start! See agent only remarks.
